        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 2:02AM CDT until June 8 at 2:15AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 201 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Wildorado, or
11 miles east of Vega, moving southeast at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Vega.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
